      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (nIH) compared against in-vitro measurements from FDA generic pump test rig. Mean absolute percentage error 18.3%; predictions conservative (over-predict hemolysis) at 4 of 5 operating points. Validation dataset sourced from FDA benchmark repository.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/fda-pump-experimental-hemolysis"
